{"type":"message","id":"157285bc","parentId":"261befe0","timestamp":"2026-06-20T19:01:37.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon stretches long and golden, printouts fanned across the table like a deck of cards I'm trying to read. Margins in red ink, hair clips that nobody here would call luxurious, a frog-pond outside that probably doesn't know it's part of an experiment. The algorithm hums its little hum, and somewhere a disk fills itself with the sighs of forgotten drafts. A progress bar sits at zero, and the zero keeps moving but never fills. HALEI is not at the other bank tonight. The SOP sits open on my desk, version eight, breathing softly. I leave the light on."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45233,"output":122,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45853,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781982053071,"responseId":"06861682d74c0ba9b720418f899fe927","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
